[Spectrum Modem] 
      │  (WAN, public IP from Spectrum)
      ▼
[VLAN-Capable Router / Firewall]   ← pfSense / OPNsense box, UniFi, MikroTik, etc.
      │
      ├──> [Orbi in AP Mode]  ← Wi-Fi for family (SSID = Home, Guest, etc.)
      │
      └──> [Ethernet Run to Your Room]
                │
          [Managed Switch]
                ├──> Your PC (access port, VLAN 20 maybe)
                └──> Proxmox Server (trunk port, carries VLAN 10/20/30)
